1
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,800
I'm honored by the presence

2
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:25,060
of you and the Second Young Master today.

3
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,880
It seems our last cooperation was pleasant,

4
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:28,640
wasn't it?

5
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,600
That's all in the past.

6
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,170
Let's not bring it up again.

7
00:01:33,880 --> 00:01:35,920
That's not quite right.

8
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,610
After all, the Second Young Master

9
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:41,039
hasn't taken over the Lu family yet.

10
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:43,000
Cutting off our cooperation now

11
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:44,520
would be a pity.

12
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:47,240
Mr. Shen, just say what's on your mind.

13
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,720
You are a smart woman.

14
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:54,680
You should know the Shen family's foundation.

15
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,720
Although we can't compare to the Lu family,

16
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,520
but the connections and resources

17
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,920
we hold now

18
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:04,320
are enough to influence the Lu family's situation.

19
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:07,920
Now there is a rift within the Lu family.

20
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:11,080
Whichever side the Shen family takes,

21
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,000
that side

22
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,260
is more likely to be the ultimate winner.

23
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:19,079
Lu Jingheng is an ungrateful bastard.

24
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,120
However, the Second Young Master

25
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:24,680
looks like someone who can achieve great things.

26
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,440
I might as well change course

27
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:30,240
and help the Second Young Master seize power in the Lu family.

28
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:32,800
I wonder what you two think.

29
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:38,120
You think too highly of yourself.

30
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:39,400
Everyone knows

31
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,040
the Shen Group has been going downhill.

32
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,600
You've lost project after project.

33
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,000
You can't even

34
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,400
save yourselves now.

35
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:49,380
How can you talk about helping me take power?

36
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:51,600
Boy, watch your mouth.

37
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,880
You should remember,

38
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,400
a starved camel is still bigger than a horse.

39
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,680
Otherwise, Old Master Lu

40
00:02:57,680 --> 00:03:00,120
wouldn't have arranged a marriage with our Shen family.

41
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,080
Besides,

42
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:02,680
with your limited skills,

43
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,410
how can you compare to your older brother?

44
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,160
Sit down.

45
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:14,040
Mr. Shen, what do you want?

46
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,680
It's very simple.

47
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,400
As long as you can persuade

48
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,920
those old shareholders of the Lu family

49
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:22,120
to bring our Shen family onto the board,

50
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,800
I promise that within a year,

51
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:27,520
I will help the second son sideline Lu Jingheng.

52
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,520
By then,

53
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,880
the Lu family will belong to you two.

54
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,400
This matter

55
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,520
isn't too difficult.

56
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:38,480
But why should I trust you?

57
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:41,520
My dear in-law.

58
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,880
My proof of loyalty,

59
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:46,240
didn't you receive it long ago?

60
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,250
What do you mean?

61
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,880
Who do you think gave you

62
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,480
Shen Zhixia's medical records?

63
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,640
Shen Jingyao.

64
00:03:58,320 --> 00:04:00,720
His acting is getting better and better.

65
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,840
Shen Jingyao is an old fox.

66
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:09,280
We need to be careful of him from now on.

67
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,320
Understood, Mom.

68
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:13,120
He would even betray his own daughter.

69
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,840
There's nothing he wouldn't do.

70
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,240
But he's easy to control.

71
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:18,279
As long as we firmly hold what he wants

72
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,720
and occasionally give him a little taste,

73
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,649
he won't turn against us so easily.

74
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,320
If this old man

75
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:25,250
is a fish dying of thirst right now,

76
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:26,980
then the water in our hands

77
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,320
is his only hope.

78
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,340
What has your good brother

79
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,320
been busy with at the company lately?

80
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:35,580
He is in no mood to manage the company now.

81
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,200
He stays at home every day with his crazy wife,

82
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,320
never leaving her side.

83
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,520
Such an important meeting,

84
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,080
he canceled it just like that.

85
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,120
In your words,

86
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,600
he is now just

87
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,600
a piece of trash tied down by a woman,

88
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,440
unable to make any waves.

89
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:50,080
Son, remember what Mom said.

90
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,920
Better safe than sorry.

91
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,680
Come on, drink it.

92
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,120
Son,

93
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:21,320
I've done everything you asked.

94
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:23,000
Please let me off.

95
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:25,120
Untie me, okay?

96
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,040
Don't worry.

97
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,240
Drink before we talk.

98
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:31,400
What, afraid to drink?

99
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:33,120
Afraid I poisoned it?

100
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,600
Didn't I tell you?

101
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,880
I need you to help me deal with Su Manyun and her son.

102
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,240
Why would I poison you?

103
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:42,360
We live in a society of law. I don't kill people.

104
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:44,880
It's been three days.

105
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:46,740
Are you trying to starve to death?

106
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,560
I dismissed everyone in the house.

107
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,720
It's just the two of us left.

108
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:52,000
If you want to starve to death, don't drink it.

109
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,800
But you don't seem to have any other choice, do you?

110
00:05:56,800 --> 00:06:00,480
Do you want to end up in jail?

111
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,920
See? I told you it would be fine.

112
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,800
Young Master.

113
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,400
Young Madam thinks today's medicine is too bitter.

114
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,280
Go to the kitchen, make a cup of honey water,

115
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,520
and bring it to her bedroom.

116
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,280
Make sure you watch her

117
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:32,080
drink the medicine with the honey water.

118
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,680
Okay, I'll go get it done now.

119
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,920
Did the plan succeed?

120
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,600
Now that you have Su Manyun

121
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:11,080
and the evidence of her betraying the Lu family.

122
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,280
Let Dad go.

123
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,080
Let him off.

124
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,720
Do you now understand

125
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:20,600
what it feels like to slowly torture someone to death?

126
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:23,180
Just like what you did to my mom back then.

127
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:30,680
You still called the police.

128
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,520
Are you trying to get Dad killed?

129
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:34,850
Going back on your word.

130
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,800
I learned it from you, Dad.

131
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,040
Ingrate.

132
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,880
You are such an ingrate.

133
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:42,800
I raised you since you were little.

134
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,720
Was that glass of milk good?

135
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,740
Did you put something in the milk?

136
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,880
Take a guess.

137
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:08,880
Ms. Shen,

138
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,000
your father, Shen Jingyao,

139
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,840
claims that you poisoned his milk.

140
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:13,840
He must be paranoid.

141
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:14,640
Me?

142
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:15,880
Poison?

143
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:17,280
Is that even possible?

144
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,080
But he kept saying that

145
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,400
after drinking the milk you gave him,

146
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,880
he felt severe physical discomfort.

147
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:21,720
Officer,

148
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,480
he isn't poisoned.

149
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,000
He's just done too many bad things

150
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,520
and scared himself sick.

151
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,640
If you don't believe me,

152
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:29,280
you can give him a checkup.

153
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,680
Letting someone who fears death

154
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,880
live anytime and anywhere

155
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:36,120
in the agony of an impending death

156
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,610
is more satisfying than just killing him.

157
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,200
I just want him to

158
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:43,480
taste the pain bit by bit

159
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:47,320
and experience the suffering you went through back then.

160
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,720
Rest assured.

161
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,000
This is just the interest.

162
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,800
For what they did to you and your mother,

163
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:39,880
I'll make them pay back in full with interest.

164
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:45,120
Brother, it's so late.

165
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,000
If it's just some trivial matter,

166
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,600
let Dad get some rest.

167
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:52,240
Jingheng, go ahead.

168
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,600
Whether it's a trivial matter,

169
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,330
Dad will know once he sees this.

170
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,800
Look at what you've done.

171
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,920
What did I do?

172
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,720
Why are you so angry?

173
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,080
See for yourself.

174
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,560
Zhenye.

175
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,530
There must be a misunderstanding.

176
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,580
Someone is trying to frame me.

177
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,800
You know.

178
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,570
I never get involved in the Lu family's business.

179
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:43,280
I'll call the lawyer right now

180
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,330
and have him look into this matter.

181
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,480
A misunderstanding?

182
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,520
Stepmother,

183
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:51,800
I see you won't give up until the bitter end.

184
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,740
Lu Jingheng, what do you mean?

185
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:55,440
I'm telling you, just say what you want.

186
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:57,000
Stop being so pretentious.

187
00:10:57,000 --> 00:11:00,080
Are you trying to frame my mom with some broken contracts?

188
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:02,000
You make it sound like I'm guilty.

189
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,240
The Lu family has its rules.

190
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:06,160
Just based on your words,

191
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:07,720
you want to convict me?

192
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:09,680
As long as you can sway

193
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:11,200
the old shareholders of the Lu family

194
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,330
and get our Shen family onto the board,

195
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,170
I guarantee that within a year,

196
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:17,640
I'll help the Second Young Master sideline Lu Jingheng.

197
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:18,720
When that time comes,

198
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:21,180
the Lu family will belong to you and your son.

199
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:23,240
Dad, after listening to this recording,

200
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:26,680
do you still think this is just a misunderstanding?

201
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:29,520
I bet Stepmom will definitely say

202
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:31,280
that since Shen Jingyao and I are father and daughter,

203
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:33,280
we must have colluded on all of this.

204
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:37,200
It's a pity Shen Jingyao has too much dirt on him.

205
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:39,080
Otherwise, I would have locked him up long ago.

206
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,600
If you want a confrontation, fine.

207
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,720
Ask the police,

208
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,520
and see if they can

209
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:46,800
or will help you cover up this lie.

210
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,080
Shen Zhixia.

211
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,280
You set me up.

212
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,280
Shut up!

213
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,240
Kneel!

214
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:57,320
Kneel down.

215
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,120
Zhenye.

216
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:03,280
It was Shen Jingyao who told me

217
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:05,040
about the board of directors.

218
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:08,720
I never thought of harming the Lu family's interests.

219
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:10,280
I never did.

220
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:13,040
I just saw our son at the company

221
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,720
being left out every day.

222
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:16,280
I was anxious.

223
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:20,570
You gave all the good projects, connections, and resources

224
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,200
to Jingheng.

225
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:23,920
Jingxi is at the company,

226
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:26,240
but he doesn't even have a say.

227
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,280
I was wrong.

228
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,920
It was Shen Jingyao.

229
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:38,040
Shen Jingyao said

230
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:41,000
he was willing to support Jingxi.

231
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,520
I thought

232
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:44,600
if he could work at the company,

233
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:47,320
it would be good for you to see his abilities.

234
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,840
I was just confused,

235
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,720
believed his nonsense,

236
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:56,530
and harmed the Lu family's interests.

237
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:58,720
Zhenye,

238
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:03,520
for the sake of my deep love for our child,

239
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,200
please don't be harsh on Jingxi.

240
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,520
You...

241
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,720
You've gone too far.

242
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,240
From today on,

243
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:17,740
all your and Jingxi's shares in the Lu Group will be taken back.

244
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:21,120
You are forbidden to touch any company affairs.

245
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:23,920
Dad, you're confused.

246
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:24,920
It's obviously them...

247
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:25,680
Shut up!

248
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:29,800
Zhenye, don't be angry.

249
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,200
It's all my fault.

250
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:33,000
I didn't teach Jingxi well.

251
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,000
It is my fault.

252
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,080
I promise you.

253
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:39,000
From now on, Jingxi and I will behave ourselves

254
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,280
and never interfere in company affairs again.

255
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:42,200
We won't.

256
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,520
We really won't.

257
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:44,800
Jingheng.

258
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:47,080
About today...

259
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:49,840
You clean up the mess.

260
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,680
Dismissed.

261
00:14:33,160 --> 00:14:33,420
Cast

262
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:34,120
Shen Zhixia Liao Huijia

263
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:34,440
Lu Jingheng Deng Chaoyuan

264
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,080
Lu Jingxi Liu Yufeng

265
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:35,760
Wen Shuyi Zheng Nanxi

266
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:36,360
Wen Zhuocheng Wang Ye

267
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:36,680
Su Yuran Ma Jie

